name: Outta' 51
description:
As a recent visitor to earth, you have found yourself captured within the grounds of area 51. Play as the alien and complete puzzles whilst avoiding capture by the scientists that are looking for you in increasing harder levels. Can you get Outta' 51? 

This is in early development and we as a team looking if this early beta is successful. Let us know what details you'd like added or don't like!

Thank you,  

From the Developers
